        "content": "<p>Virto Commerce philosophy is based on the idea that making gradual changes is the only way to overcome the enterprise complexity described above. Virto Commerce platform is designed in a way to facilitate this approach.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Customizable &amp; Extensible Platform and Modular architecture makes possible to start acting locally (in terms of regions, functions, processes) and continue by gradual extending the solution, adding new stakeholders, regions, functions, integrations.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Small projects reduce a quantity of affected stakeholders on each step and come to the situation when each small step is not critical for most of stakeholders, so that you can keep high implementation speed.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Virto Commerce is very efficient in building a flexible and well maintainable multi-layer platforms for multi-regional companies. Experience of our customers proofs the efficiency of starting to build a few local VC solutions and then generalizing common rules, practices, integrations and requirements in a more generic platform.</p>\n\n<p>Virto Commerce is an API-based modular solution. It can be embedded into any process or replace any function without running a huge project. You can start substituting your legacy systems, improve the process structure or add new functionality without creating additional risks.</p>\n",
